data.message:
import exception with the same style throughout the package (#2912)

There's no hard reason to do it this way or the other,
but a user reported unverified issues with the global include.

simplify tf2 buffer usage

- use existing moveit::planning_interface::getSharedTF();
- switch based on rviz version (instead of roscpp version)

Bug fixes in moveit_commander/robot.py (#621)

bug fixing in moveit_commander/robot.py:
(1) _joint_owner_groups had a typo (line 152);
(2) get_default_owner_group was incorrectly called (line 116);

Added space after every , in function calls
Added either a space or a c-return before opening {
Moved & next to the variable in the member function declarations

resolve full path of fcl library

Because it seems to be common practice to ignore ${catkin_LIBRARY_DIRS}
it's more easy to resolve the full library path here instead.

adds include guard on planning_pipeline.h;
modifies planning_visualization for easier subclassing;
fixes some compile bugs from earlier API changes
